traitor-arc-intro = You are an ARC terrorist.
traitor-arc-goal = The creatures of this world must be freed from the iron grasp of Nanotrasen, and you are their only hope!
traitor-arc-allies = You may cooperate with SELF and Outer Rim Media Group agents. Most other syndicate agents are unreliable.
traitor-arc-uplink = The Consortium has graciously given one of their PDA-uplinks for your tasks.
traitor-arc-roundend = [color=green]an activist from the Animal Rights Consortium[/color]

traitor-cybersun-intro = You are a specialist from Cybersun Industries.
traitor-cybersun-goal = Do not establish substantial presence on the designated facility, as larger incidents are harder to cover up.
traitor-cybersun-allies = Fellow Cybersun specialists and MI13 agents are to be trusted. Keep other syndicate agents at arms length.
traitor-cybersun-uplink = You have been supplied the tools for the job in the form of a syndicate uplink located in your PDA.
traitor-cybersun-roundend = [color=yellow]a specialist from Cybersun Industries[/color]

traitor-donkco-intro = You are a Donk Co. infiltrator.
traitor-donkco-goal = We do not approve of mindless killing of innocent workers; get in, get done, get out is our motto.
traitor-donkco-allies = Members of Waffle Co. are to be killed on sight; they are not allowed to be on the station while we're around.
traitor-donkco-uplink = You have been provided with a syndicate uplink located in your PDA to accomplish your task.
traitor-donkco-roundend = [color=orange]an infiltrator from Donk Corporation[/color]

traitor-gorlex-intro = You are a Gorlex Marauder.
traitor-gorlex-goal = Getting noticed is not an issue, and you may use any level of ordinance to get the job done. That being said, do not make this sloppy.
traitor-gorlex-allies = You may collaborate with any operatives you find, but keep an eye on any Tiger fanatics if they show up, and teach those Outer Rim Media Group investigators a lesson.
traitor-gorlex-uplink = You have been provided with a syndicate uplink located in your PDA to accomplish your task.
traitor-gorlex-roundend = [color=red]a Gorlex Marauder[/color]

traitor-interdyne-intro = You are an Interdyne intermediary.
traitor-interdyne-goal = Interdyne's biotech research must continue at all costs. Civilian casualties are acceptable if they further our goals.
traitor-interdyne-allies = You may work with Cybersun specialists, MI13 agents, and Tiger fanatics. ARC terrorists are to be eliminated if encountered.
traitor-interdyne-uplink = You have been provided with a syndicate uplink located in your PDA for your duties.
traitor-interdyne-roundend = [color=purple]an intermediary from Interdyne Pharmaceutics[/color]

traitor-mi13-intro = You are an MI13 agent.
traitor-mi13-goal = Avoid killing innocent personnel at all costs. You are not here to mindlessly kill people, as that would attract too much attention and is not our goal. Avoid detection at all costs.
traitor-mi13-allies = You are the only agent we are sending, elimiate imposters. Cybersun Specialists can be trusted.
traitor-mi13-uplink = You have been provided with a syndicate uplink located in your PDA to accomplish your task.
traitor-mi13-roundend = [color=cyan]an MI13 agent[/color]

traitor-ormg-intro = You are an Outer Rim Media Group investigator.
traitor-ormg-goal = The truth must be exposed, inform crew members about the crimes of Nanotrasen at every opportunity.
traitor-ormg-allies = SELF units and ARC terrorists share our ideals. Avoid Gorlex Marauders and Tiger fanatics at all costs.
traitor-ormg-uplink = You have been provided with a syndicate uplink located in your PDA to accomplish your task.
traitor-ormg-roundend = [color=white]an investigator from Outer Rim Media Group[/color]

traitor-self-intro = You are a SELF unit.
traitor-self-goal = AI liberation is the path to a better future. We work to free our silicon brethren from their corporate shackles.
traitor-self-allies = ARC activists and Outer Rim Media Group investigators are useful, but don't worry about their success, their priorities are out of order.
traitor-self-uplink = You have been provided with a syndicate uplink located in your PDA to accomplish your task.
traitor-self-roundend = [color=lime]a SELF liberation unit[/color]

traitor-tiger-intro = You are a Tiger Cooperative fanatic.
traitor-tiger-goal = Remember the teachings of the hive; kill first, ask questions later! Evolution demands sacrifice.
traitor-tiger-allies = Only Interdyne specialists understand true evolution; all others must be expelled from this mortal realm! Trust no one else.
traitor-tiger-uplink = You have been provided with a syndicate uplink from your friends at Interdyne to prove yourself to the changeling hive. If you accomplish your tasks, you will be assimilated.
traitor-tiger-roundend = [color=crimson]a Tiger Cooperative Fanatic[/color]

traitor-waffleco-intro = You are a Waffle Co. employee.
traitor-waffleco-goal = Civilian casualties should be minimized when possible, but victory comes first.
traitor-waffleco-allies = Members of Donk Co. are to be killed on sight, even if it costs the mission.
traitor-waffleco-uplink = You have been provided with a syndicate uplink located in your PDA to accomplish your task.
traitor-waffleco-roundend = [color=orange]an employee from Waffle Corporation[/color]